NK033(gi)003:1: // klong sde rdo rje zam pa'i byin rlabs kyi cho ga rgyas pa khrigs su bkod pa bzhugs /
NK033(gi)003:2: na mo gu ru bud+d+ha bo d+hi sat+wa /
NK033(gi)003:3: sgom ma smin pa smin par byed pa'i /
NK033(gi)003:4: tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs la /
NK033(gi)003:5: sbyor dngos 'di la don gsum ste /
NK033(gi)003:6: rnam gnyis rjes kyi cho ga dang gsum mo //
NK033(gi)003:9: sgrib pa sbyang ba'i sbyin zhi ba'i sreg bya'o //
NK033(gi)003:10: man+dala de nas gnas khang shin tu legs par bcos la /
NK033(gi)003:12: bdud rtsi lnga sogs ba'i chag chag btab //
NK033(gi)003:16: gu lang da la'i dbus ser po /
NK033(gi)003:22: de 'i nang du rdo rje'i gdan zur drug pa /
NK033(gi)003:24: bud+d+ha he ru ka mngon rdzogs yab yum bskyed //
NK033(gi)003:25: shar man+dala de'i phyogs kyi zhing khams /
NK033(gi)003:30: nub nub phyogs kyi zhing khams /
NK033(gi)003:32: byang phyogs kyi zhing khams ljang gu'o //
NK033(gi)003:34: man+dala de'i mu ran gyi kha dog de dag ni //
NK033(gi)003:35: phyogs shar dmar lho ljang nub dkar byang mthing kha'o //
NK033(gi)003:36: las ldog la bri bar bya //
NK033(gi)003:37: de nas bum pa man+dala gyi dbus su /
NK033(gi)003:39: rin zangs gser med na rdza la bya /
NK033(gi)003:40: po che sogs bum pa la //
NK033(gi)003:41: nag shin tu dag par bkrus la /
NK033(gi)003:42: po ra ri med par bya //
NK033(gi)003:43: gu gul bum pa de la /
NK033(gi)003:45: sum bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i sngags ring gis /
NK033(gi)003:46: b+ha ni sogs bgegs kyang bskrad //
NK033(gi)003:47: srog chags med pa'i chu yis gtsang ma /
NK033(gi)003:49: rin chen lnga dang 'bru sna lnga //
NK033(gi)003:50: 'bras so ba sran ma nas gro /
NK033(gi)003:51: bzang po drug dang snying po mar bu ram sbrang rtsi /
NK033(gi)003:53: tsan+dana la sogs pa'i yang dri bzang bstsal //
NK033(gi)003:58: bcas pho brang nas steng du lte bar gzhug /
NK033(gi)003:59: de nas bum pa'i steng du /
NK033(gi)003:60: ka p+aa dum bu gcig pa /
NK033(gi)003:62: sin+d+hu ra sogs chos 'byung bsnol ma'i dbus su /
NK033(gi)003:63: man+dala rtsibs drug la +aah h+aum h+r+aihb+h+r+aumhham zhes bri /
NK033(gi)003:65: chang ka p+aa la'i nang du blugs la a mri ta yis bran //
NK033(gi)003:66: shar ka p+aa la'i mdun ngos /
NK033(gi)003:67: phyogs su bstan la bum steng bzhugs //
NK033(gi)003:69: de nas ka p+aa la'i steng du /
NK033(gi)003:70: me long la bzhengs pa ni /
NK033(gi)003:71: sin+d+ha ra yi man+dala chos 'byung bsnol mar bris la dbus su /
NK033(gi)003:72: rtsibs drug la +aaham ham h+aum h+r+aihb+h+r+aum bris /
NK033(gi)003:74: yi ge bdun pa'i sngags kyis brgyan //
NK033(gi)003:78: da byid dkar po gcig thub /
NK033(gi)003:80: ka ra dkar po rnams mar la rta byas la sbyar /
NK033(gi)003:87: bu ram dang sbyar ba bcas thig la dkar dmar gyi skyobs yin /
NK033(gi)003:90: bdud rtsi byas la me long steng du /
NK033(gi)003:93: dkar dmar dar bdud rtsi ril bu de /
NK033(gi)003:95: ka p+aa la yi steng du bzhugs //
NK033(gi)003:97: gzhan yang mkho dang por ba'i yo byad ni //
NK033(gi)003:99: tshogs dang sha la sogs pa'i khyad par gtor mkha' 'gro ma gsum la /
NK033(gi)003:102: sha chen khrag dang zhag chen gyi gtor ma /
NK033(gi)003:104: dkar gsum mngar gsum gtor ma'o //
NK033(gi)003:105: khyad par mar me mtshan thub gsum //
NK033(gi)003:107: 'bru dang zhun chen gyi rtsi mar ro //
NK033(gi)003:109: mchod pa lnga dang me tog spos mar me dri chab zhal zas /
NK033(gi)003:111: dar gyi cod pan srung skud dang mda' chung gzhu rnams sogs //
NK033(gi)003:112: tshul shing dang sgom thag dang sgom rten dang kun //
NK033(gi)003:113: mkho ba'i yo byad tshang bar bshams //
NK033(gi)003:114: skabs 'dir rang gzhan gyi don du phyi nang gi rgya mtsho khrus lung /
NK033(gi)003:115: sngon du 'gro ba 'thad par sems pas zur du bkol ba ltar ro //
NK033(gi)003:121: byin rlabs dang po rnam pa gnyis kyis yin te //
NK033(gi)003:122: man+dala dang ni byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK033(gi)003:125: dang po de la man+dala byin gyis rlabs par bya /
NK033(gi)003:127: dbus man+dala kyi gu lang ser po'i steng //
NK033(gi)003:128: gu ni ser po gcig tu bsam //
NK033(gi)003:129: gu lang man+dala h+aum zhes brjod //
NK033(gi)003:131: gser gyi sa gzhir gyur par bsam //
NK033(gi)003:132: phyi yi man+dala de'i sna tshogs pad+ma la //
NK033(gi)003:133: pam ni dmar po gcig tu bsam //
NK033(gi)003:134: pam pad+ma man+dala zhes brjod do //
NK033(gi)003:135: sna kha dog tshogs pad+mara gyur par bsam //
NK033(gi)003:136: de 'i nang du mu khyud dkar po la //
NK033(gi)003:137: a ni dkar po gcig tu bsam //
NK033(gi)003:138: a tsan+d+ra man+dala zhes brjod pas //
NK033(gi)003:141: de yi mu khyud dmar po'i steng //
NK033(gi)003:142: ma ni dmar po gcig tu bsam //
NK033(gi)003:143: ma s+aur+ya man+dala zhes brjod pas //
NK033(gi)003:146: de dbus chos 'byung nag po'i ba ni dmar po gcig tu bsam /
NK033(gi)003:149: ba ni mthing kha gcig tu bsam //
NK033(gi)003:151: ba ti tish+tha zhes brjod pas //
NK033(gi)003:152: ba ti sngon po'i gdan gcig bsam //
NK033(gi)003:153: de 'i steng ba ti dmar po'i steng //
NK033(gi)003:154: du ba ti tish+tha zhes brjod pas //
NK033(gi)003:155: ba ti dmar po gcig tu bsam //
NK033(gi)003:156: de'i dbus kyi pad+ma ge sar steng //
NK033(gi)003:157: yi ge b+h+r+aum gcig bsam par bya //
NK033(gi)003:159: sna tshogs pad+ma'i ge sar du bsam //
NK033(gi)003:161: shar gyi phyogs man+dala dkar po'i steng //
NK033(gi)003:162: ke ni dkar po gcig bsam ste //
NK033(gi)003:163: ke ru man+dala zhes zhing khams brjod pas //
NK033(gi)003:164: kee ru dkar po'i zhing khams bsam //
NK033(gi)003:165: lho zhing khams yi man+dala sngon po'i steng //
NK033(gi)003:166: bee ni mthing kha gcig tu bsam //
NK033(gi)003:167: bee d+aur+ya man+dala zhes brjod pas //
NK033(gi)003:168: bee d+aur+ya yi zhing khams bsam //
NK033(gi)003:169: nub phyogs zhing khams man+dala dmar po'i steng //
NK033(gi)003:170: pam ni dmar po gcig bsam ste //
NK033(gi)003:171: pam pad+ma man+dala zhes brjod pas //
NK033(gi)003:172: pad+ma r+aa ga'i zhing khams bsam //
NK033(gi)003:173: byang phyogs zhing khams man+dala ljang khu'i steng //
NK033(gi)003:174: e ni ljang khu gcig bsam ste //
NK033(gi)003:175: in+d+ra n+ai la man+dala zhes brjod pas //
NK033(gi)003:176: in+d+ra n+ai la'i zhing khams bsam //
NK033(gi)003:177: de nas rdzas gsum bum pa thod pa me long gsum /
NK033(gi)003:179: dbus kyi pad+ma'i sna tshogs ge sar gyi steng //
NK033(gi)003:180: du bum pa bzhugs pa'i nang du ni //
NK033(gi)003:181: kha dog lnga thig le mthing kha /
NK033(gi)003:189: phyogs bcu'i bde bar gshegs pa yi //
NK033(gi)003:190: thugs dam rgyud ni bskul nas su //
NK033(gi)003:191: sku yi 'od zer rnam pa lnga //
NK033(gi)003:192: dbu yi gtsug tor las thon nas //
NK033(gi)003:193: bum pa'i nang du byon par bsam //
NK033(gi)003:194: de la shes pa ma yengs par //
NK033(gi)003:195: snying po 'di ni brjod par bya //
NK033(gi)003:196: sh+r+ai badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro
NK033(gi)003:197: d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo
NK033(gi)003:198: h+aum / de la stong tsam them pa dang //
NK033(gi)003:199: de steng ka p+aa la yi nang //
NK033(gi)003:200: a ni dmar ser gcig bsgom ste //
NK033(gi)003:202: phyogs bcu'i bde bar gshegs pa yi //
NK033(gi)003:203: thugs dam rgyud ni bskul nas su //
NK033(gi)003:204: ljags kyi dbang po las thon nas //
NK033(gi)003:205: ka p+aa la ru babs par bsgom //
NK033(gi)003:206: de la shes pa ma yengs par //
NK033(gi)003:207: gsung gi snying po 'di brjod do //
NK033(gi)003:208: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK033(gi)003:209: de la stong tsam them pa dang //
NK033(gi)003:210: de steng me long nang du ni //
NK033(gi)003:211: ham ni dkar po gcig bsgom ste //
NK033(gi)003:213: bde gshegs thugs dam rgyud bskul nas //
NK033(gi)003:214: 'od zer thugs ka nas thon nas //
NK033(gi)003:215: me long thog tu babs par bsgom //
NK033(gi)003:216: de la shes pa ma yengs par //
NK033(gi)003:217: thugs kyi snying po 'di brjod do //
NK033(gi)003:219: sku gsung thugs kyi sngags de dag /
NK033(gi)003:220: bar chad med par bzlas pa na //
NK033(gi)003:221: ye shes spyan drangs dam tshig ni //
NK033(gi)003:222: gnyis su med par gyur par bsgom /
NK033(gi)003:223: gnyis pa cho ga'i rim pa ni //
NK033(gi)003:224: sbyor ba dngos gzhi rnam pa gnyis //
NK033(gi)003:225: dang po sbyor ba bstan pa ni //
NK033(gi)003:226: bka' bsgo bden pa brdar bar bya //
NK033(gi)003:227: de nas bgegs ni mthar byed dang //
NK033(gi)003:228: khro bo las ni thams cad pas //
NK033(gi)003:229: bgegs dang bar chad bsal bar bya //
NK033(gi)003:230: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha ha la ha la h'u /
NK033(gi)003:231: sum b+ha ni be ga ba ti rak+sha rak+sha h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:232: lnga'am bdun gyis bgegs bskrad do //
NK033(gi)003:233: de nas mtshams ni bcad par bya //
NK033(gi)003:234: yi dam gzhung yang bsrang bar bya //
NK033(gi)003:235: tshogs kyi mchod pa bzang po bya //
NK033(gi)003:236: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed cho ga bya //
NK033(gi)003:237: rjes la 'byung po'i gtor ma gtong //
NK033(gi)003:238: zhes pa de yan chad kyis sgom tshul bla ma'i
NK033(gi)003:239: byin rlabs rgyas pa'i sbyor ba'i rim pa rdzogs so
NK033(gi)003:240: //// he ru ka mngon rdzogs rgyal po'i phrin las bzhugs /
NK033(gi)003:241: bcom ldan 'das he ru ka mngon rdzogs rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)003:242: de la bsgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK033(gi)003:243: gnas dben par dkyil 'khor gyi steng du /
NK033(gi)003:244: mchod pa rnam pa lnga bdud rtsi ba ling rak+ta bshams la /
NK033(gi)003:245: stan bde ba la 'dug ste skyabs 'gro dang byams
NK033(gi)003:246: dang snying rje byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de
NK033(gi)003:247: / bla ma rdo rje slob dpon dang phyogs bcu
NK033(gi)003:248: na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'
NK033(gi)003:249: / / dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i khyad par dang /
NK033(gi)003:250: gsang sngags yang dag gi lha tshogs bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK033(gi)003:251: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung
NK033(gi)003:252: nas snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du
NK033(gi)003:254: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)003:255: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK033(gi)003:259: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)003:260: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par
NK033(gi)003:261: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa la skyabs su
NK033(gi)003:262: mchi'o // mkhyen rab kyi bdag po 'phags pa 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)003:263: thugs rje'i bdag po spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)003:264: mthu stobs kyi bdag po dpal phyag na rdo rje la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)003:265: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK033(gi)003:266: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)003:267: dngos bshams yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK033(gi)003:268: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)003:269: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK033(gi)003:270: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK033(gi)003:271: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK033(gi)003:272: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK033(gi)003:273: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK033(gi)003:274: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK033(gi)003:275: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK033(gi)003:276: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi'o //
NK033(gi)003:277: bskul ba'i sa las bzhengs nas kyang //
NK033(gi)003:278: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul //
NK033(gi)003:279: ma grol ba ni rnam grol phyir //
NK033(gi)003:281: bdag la gnas pa'i lus 'di ni //
NK033(gi)003:282: bde bar gshegs pa rnams la 'bul //
NK033(gi)003:283: tshe rabs bsags pa'i las rnams kun //
NK033(gi)003:284: bsdus te byang chub mchog tu bsngo //
NK033(gi)003:285: bsod nams 'di yis thams cad gzigs pa nyid //
NK033(gi)003:286: thob nas nyes pa'i dgra rnams bcom byas te //
NK033(gi)003:287: skye rga na 'chi'i rba klong 'khrugs pa yi //
NK033(gi)003:288: srid pa'i mtsho las 'gro ba sgrol bar shog /
NK033(gi)003:290: de nas lung rnam pa bdun gyis nub gcig gis phrin las gzhung bsrang ba la /
NK033(gi)003:291: dang po bgegs bsrung ba 'bar ba mtshams kyi lung du mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK033(gi)003:292: bdag nyid dpal chen du gsal bar bskyed de /
NK033(gi)003:294: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK033(gi)003:295: yang dag don la mi brtson zhing //
NK033(gi)003:296: 'byung po dam med thams cad kun //
NK033(gi)003:297: rang rang gnas su bde bar dengs //
NK033(gi)003:299: bcom ldan dpal chen khros nas ni //
NK033(gi)003:300: bar chad sbyor ba thal bar rlog /
NK033(gi)003:301: mtshon cha 'bar ba'i gur gyis gtams //
NK033(gi)003:302: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u phata /
NK033(gi)003:306: k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK033(gi)003:307: rang dpal he ru ka'i thugs ka nas 'od 'phros /
NK033(gi)003:309: phyogs mtshams thams cad ra ba dang gur gyi gtams par gyur pa'i phyi la me ri'o //
NK033(gi)003:310: a ko ta ya mung+ga ra h'u phata /
NK033(gi)003:312: ces mtshon cha lngas mtshams bcad /
NK033(gi)003:315: steng yang rdo rje'i bla bre la //
NK033(gi)003:316: rdo rje'i thog dang ser chen 'bebs //
NK033(gi)003:317: 'og kyang rdo rje'i sa gzhi la //
NK033(gi)003:318: rdo rje'i sa gzhi gcal du bkram //
NK033(gi)003:319: bar snang rdo rje'i sprin phung 'khrigs //
NK033(gi)003:321: rdo rje'i glog 'khyug khyugs se khyug /
NK033(gi)003:322: rdo rje'i thog 'bebs lams se lam //
NK033(gi)003:323: rdo rje'i me 'bar ya la la //
NK033(gi)003:324: rdo rje'i tsh+wa tsh+wa skar ltar 'khrugs //
NK033(gi)003:325: phyogs mtshams steng 'og thams cad kun //
NK033(gi)003:326: thams cad rdo rje 'bar bas gtams //
NK033(gi)003:327: rdo rjes gtams pa'i gzhal yas 'dir //
NK033(gi)003:329: chu la zag pa'i gseng med cing //
NK033(gi)003:331: nyon cing bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK033(gi)003:334: bcom ldan dpal chen khros nas ni //
NK033(gi)003:335: bar chad sbyor ba thal bar rlog /
NK033(gi)003:336: rdo rje 'bar ba'i gur gyis gtams //
NK033(gi)003:338: steng yang 'khor lo'i bla bre la //
NK033(gi)003:341: steng yang ral gri'i bla bre la //
NK033(gi)003:342: ral gri'i thog dang ser chen 'bebs //
NK033(gi)003:344: steng yang phur pa'i bla bre la //
NK033(gi)003:345: phur pa'i thog dang ser chen 'bebs //
NK033(gi)003:347: steng yang tho ba'i bla bre la //
NK033(gi)003:348: tho ba'i thog dang ser chen 'bebs //
NK033(gi)003:349: 'og kyang tho ba'i sa gzhi la //
NK033(gi)003:350: tho ba'i sa gzhi gcal du bkram //
NK033(gi)003:351: bar snang tho ba'i sprin phung 'khrigs //
NK033(gi)003:353: tho ba'i glog 'khyug khyugs se khyug /
NK033(gi)003:354: tho ba'i thog 'bebs lams se lam //
NK033(gi)003:355: tho ba'i me 'bar ya la la //

NK033(gi)003:359: tho bas gtams pa'i gzhal yas 'dir //
NK033(gi)003:361: chu la zag pa'i gseng med cing //
NK033(gi)003:363: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK033(gi)003:366: bcom ldan dpal chen khros nas ni //
NK033(gi)003:367: bar chad sbyor ba thal bar rlog /
NK033(gi)003:368: tho ba 'bar ba'i gur gyis gtams //
NK033(gi)003:370: me yi mtshams kyang de bzhin no //
NK033(gi)003:371: e ram phata ram dz+wa la ram /
NK033(gi)003:372: zhes pas 'bar ba me'i dbus su bsgom /
NK033(gi)003:373: de nas khro bo'i mtshams bcad bya ste /
NK033(gi)003:375: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)003:376: dbus phyogs stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)003:377: skye 'gro rtsi shing nags tshal kun //

NK033(gi)003:432: khro mo'i sprul pas sa gzhi gang //

NK033(gi)003:489: sku gsum sa la goms par bya //
NK033(gi)003:490: dang po chos kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK033(gi)003:491: dmigs pa med pa'i don gcig sgom //
NK033(gi)003:493: chos kyi dbyings kun tu snang /
NK033(gi)003:495: thams cad du ni khyab par bsam //
NK033(gi)003:497: bskal pa'i me rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK033(gi)003:500: ba'i tshogs ni bsam par bya //
NK033(gi)003:510: 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor yum lnga'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK033(gi)003:511: mngon par dga' ba'i rin chen gzhal yas khang //
NK033(gi)003:512: nyi zla pad+ma 'od kyi kha sbyor nang /
NK033(gi)003:513: e bsnol zur drug ze'u 'bru brdal ba yi //
NK033(gi)003:520: pa khyo shugs nyi zla pad+ma'i steng //
NK033(gi)003:522: mngon rdzogs rgyal po bud+d+ha he sku mdog phyag mtshan yum dang mthun /
NK033(gi)003:524: zhal gcig phyag gnyis mchan khung na kha t+w+aam ka bsnam pa'o //
NK033(gi)003:526: rin chen rgyan gyis rnam par brgyan //
NK033(gi)003:529: dbu skra cung zad mthur du 'phyangs //
NK033(gi)003:530: zhi ba'i mdangs la cung zhal zad khro //
NK033(gi)003:539: zhabs gnyis skyil krung du bzhugs pa //
NK033(gi)003:544: yum bde stobs dang byang sems ma rdo rje zhes bya /
NK033(gi)003:546: yab dang 'khril yab kyi gnya' gong du /
NK033(gi)003:548: sku mdog ser po yab dang 'dra dbu skra grol //
NK033(gi)003:550: nyid gsal ba'i e bsnol thugs ka nas //
NK033(gi)003:556: de'i mtha' ma rgya yig gis bskor ba'o //
NK033(gi)003:558: shin tu gsal bar bsgom par bya //
NK033(gi)003:559: rdo rje'i gdan dang lte ba la //
NK033(gi)003:565: ma s+aur+ya nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'od dang bcas /

NK033(gi)003:575: bee d+aur+ya lho bee d+aur+ya sngon po /
NK033(gi)003:577: pad+ma r+aa ga nub pad+ma r+aa ga dmar man+da la h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:578: in+d+ra n+ai la byang in+d+ra n+ai la ljang /
NK033(gi)003:580: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:582: bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /

NK033(gi)003:588: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /

NK033(gi)003:590: dang lnga dur khrod chas brgyad dpal ldan pa nas
NK033(gi)003:591: bltas pas / rigs lnga ru mngon sangs rgyas rigs lngas dbu rgyan ba dbus rnam snang /
NK033(gi)003:592: pa la don he ru ka gcig tu rdzogs pas na mngon rdzogs /
NK033(gi)003:593: che zhing gong na med pas na rgyal po zhes bya'o //

NK033(gi)003:604: mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs pa la gtso bo la gtso bos /
NK033(gi)003:607: mi gnas mi dmigs chos sku dag pa las //

NK033(gi)003:610: gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyis phyag 'tshal lo //

NK033(gi)003:613: lha ye shes sems dpa' dgyes nas sku gsung thugs
NK033(gi)003:614: kyis bdag dam tshig sems dpa'i lus ngag yid gsum
NK033(gi)003:615: byin gyis brlabs par bsam mo //

NK033(gi)003:623: 'khor la 'khor thim pas gzi brjid nus pa dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)003:627: de nas phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)003:629: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten thams cad na //
NK033(gi)003:630: bcom ldan dpal gyi phyag rgyar gsal //
NK033(gi)003:631: sku gsum gnyis med bde chen rgya //
NK033(gi)003:632: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:633: a la la hoh zhes so //

NK033(gi)003:817: thugs rje chags pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK033(gi)003:818: 'gro ba'i don la dmigs pa yi //
NK033(gi)003:820: bla ma bde gshegs mkha' 'gro dang //
NK033(gi)003:821: chos skyong srung ma ma lus la //
NK033(gi)003:822: brtse ba'i sems kyis 'bul lags kyi //
NK033(gi)003:823: thugs rjes dgongs la bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)003:824: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK033(gi)003:826: bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen po phul bas mnyes par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)003:828: de nas phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa ni /
NK033(gi)003:830: mi gnas dpal chen yab yum gsal gdab bo //
NK033(gi)003:831: dpal chen mngon rdzogs he ru ka /
NK033(gi)003:832: lha mo brgyad kyis bskor pa'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK033(gi)003:833: rnam dag chos sku'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK033(gi)003:834: sgyu ma'i phyag rgyar gsal la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK033(gi)003:835: ces yi ge brgya pa tshar gcig brjod /
NK033(gi)003:836: de nas kha bskang ba'i phyir bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)003:838: ye shes mkha' 'gro'i dbang phyug khro rgyal gtso //
NK033(gi)003:839: dpal chen he ru ka ni mtha' dang mnyam //
NK033(gi)003:840: dus drug chos kyi sku las ma g.yos kyang //
NK033(gi)003:841: thugs dang 'gal ba mchis na bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)003:842: ye shes lha la rtog pa mi mnga' yang //
NK033(gi)003:843: de yi 'khor du gtogs pa'i lha srin rnams //
NK033(gi)003:844: gnong zhing 'gal 'khrul mchis pa mthol lo bshags //
NK033(gi)003:845: rig 'dzin sgrub pa po ni chos nyid thugs su chud //
NK033(gi)003:846: ma rig dbang gis de ltar ma rtogs kyang //
NK033(gi)003:847: mi dge log pa'i las rnams ci bgyis pa //
NK033(gi)003:848: bstan pa srung ba rnams la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)003:849: 'da' dka' khas blang dam las g.yel gyur te //
NK033(gi)003:850: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)003:851: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)003:852: spyor sgrol mchod pa ting 'dzin ma bshams te //
NK033(gi)003:853: kro d+hi shwa ri'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)003:854: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)003:855: rdzas dang phyag rgya mngon du ma gyur te //
NK033(gi)003:856: koo r+ai ma brgyad thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)003:857: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)003:858: sha khrag mchod pa gzhung bzhin ma bshams pas //
NK033(gi)003:859: sed+ha ma brgyad thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)003:860: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)003:861: shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi ma gsal te //
NK033(gi)003:862: rta gdong sgo ma bzhi yi thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)003:863: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)003:864: yo byad tshogs nas tshogs kyi phud nyams pas //
NK033(gi)003:865: mkha' 'gro dbang phyug thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)003:866: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)003:867: tshogs la rol nas lhag ma ma lus pas //
NK033(gi)003:868: ma mo brtan ma'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)003:869: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)003:870: sku bskyed khro bo'i lus su ma gyur pas //
NK033(gi)003:871: sngags 'jug pho nya'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK033(gi)003:872: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)003:876: don lnga pa yang dag thugs kyi mngon rdzogs rgyal po la 'dzab dbul ba ni /
NK033(gi)003:877: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa'i lung du ru lu'i 'dzab bgrang ba ni /
NK033(gi)003:878: tshe 'di nyid la sangs rgyas par bya ba'i phyir du /
NK033(gi)003:879: ru lu dbyangs drug bya ste /
NK033(gi)003:880: de yang tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyi 'dren tshul /
NK033(gi)003:881: za hor rgyal po'i dbyangs kyi skad /
NK033(gi)003:883: rdo rje srin po'i ngur sgra /
NK033(gi)003:885: 'khun cing gdung ba'i dbyangs dang drug go //
NK033(gi)003:887: phreng ba sngags kyi rnal 'byor bsgom pa ni /
NK033(gi)003:888: bdag gi thugs khar sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte ba na /
NK033(gi)003:894: 'a ljang gu de'i mthar g.yas bskor du bzla bya'i sngags kyis bskor ba'o //
NK033(gi)003:896: sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)003:897: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:898: pad+ma gsung sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)003:899: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:900: badz+ra thugs sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)003:901: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:903: sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)003:904: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:906: sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)003:907: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:908: bzlas pa byed pa'i dus su gsal la dod par bzlas pa yin te /
NK033(gi)003:909: dus bzhir bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhi'i tshul du ting nge 'dzin dang ma bral bar byed pa yin pas /
NK033(gi)003:910: dang po bsnyen pa la bsnyen pa /
NK033(gi)003:914: de nas thun gnyis pa la nye ba'i bsnyen pa /
NK033(gi)003:915: thun gsum pa la sgrub pa /
NK033(gi)003:916: de nas sgrub pa chen po'o //
NK033(gi)003:917: dbang bzhi'i sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs la /
NK033(gi)003:918: bla ma'i man ngag bzhin sku gsung thugs kyi bsnyen pa bya /
NK033(gi)003:919: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:921: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:923: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:925: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:927: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:929: de la 'di btags la bargya'am stong bzlas la /
NK033(gi)003:930: a a sarba ta th+aa ga ta ya h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:931: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK033(gi)003:933: de nas me long gi nang du'ang steng du yi ge a ham dkar dmar gnyis bsam par bya'o //
NK033(gi)003:934: de yan chad sgrub thabs kyi dngos gazhi'o //
NK033(gi)003:935: skabs 'dir bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro gsum gyi gtor chog zur du bkol ba ltar bya'o //
NK033(gi)003:936: drug pa bza' ba tshogs kyi lung du tshogs 'bul ba la don bdun te /
NK033(gi)003:937: tshogs rnam pa gsum gyis sta gon bya ba /
NK033(gi)003:938: bsang thabs rnam pa gsum gyis dri ma dag par bya ba /
NK033(gi)003:939: sbyangs thabs rnam pa gsum gyi dngos po dang mtshan ma med par sbyangs pa /
NK033(gi)003:940: byin nor bu 'dod yon bdud rtsi gsum /
NK033(gi)003:941: rlabs rnam pa gsum gyis khyad par gyi rdzas su brlab pa /
NK033(gi)003:942: spro thabs rnam pa gsum gyis dmigs pa so sor bzung ba /
NK033(gi)003:943: dbul thabs rnam pa gsum gyi bdag gi don sgrub pa /
NK033(gi)003:944: sbyangs thabs rnam pa gsum gyis bdag gi phrin las bcol ba dang bdun no //
NK033(gi)003:945: byin rlabs kyi khyad par nor bu 'dod yon bdud rtsi gsum du byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK033(gi)003:946: lha tshogs spyan drangs pa ni /
NK033(gi)003:947: mi dmigs mkha' ltar dag cing khyab pa'i sku //
NK033(gi)003:948: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK033(gi)003:949: thugs rje'i ngang nyid chos sku dag pa las //
NK033(gi)003:950: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)003:952: dbang phyug chen po yab yum dang //
NK033(gi)003:953: byang chub rdo rje lcam dral dang //
NK033(gi)003:954: khro bo'i rgyal po mtha' dag dang //
NK033(gi)003:955: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK033(gi)003:956: lha dang lha min rnal 'byor pa //
NK033(gi)003:957: rnal 'byor longs spyod che la gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)003:958: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)003:963: ram ram ram ni ye shes me yin te //
NK033(gi)003:964: me yi snying po ram zhes bya //
NK033(gi)003:965: ram las ye shes me byung bas //
NK033(gi)003:966: bag chags ma lus bsreg par bya //
NK033(gi)003:968: yam yam yam ni ye shes rlung yin te //
NK033(gi)003:969: rlung gi snying po yam zhes bya //
NK033(gi)003:970: yam las ye shes rlung byung bas //
NK033(gi)003:971: bag chags ma lus gtor bar bya //
NK033(gi)003:973: kham kham kham ni ye shes chu yin te //
NK033(gi)003:974: chu yi snying po kham zhes bya //
NK033(gi)003:975: kham las ye shes chu byung bas //
NK033(gi)003:976: bag chags ma lus bkru bar bya //
NK033(gi)003:978: lhag mthong gi me yis bsregs //
NK033(gi)003:979: ye shes kyi rlung gis gtor //
NK033(gi)003:980: zhi gnas kyi chu yis bkrus so //
NK033(gi)003:981: byin gyi brlab thabs gsum ni /
NK033(gi)003:984: bdud rtsi mu tig dkar po dri ma med par byin gyis brlab bo //
NK033(gi)003:988: 'di ni shes rab ral gri ste //
NK033(gi)003:989: rin chen gter kha 'byed pa dang //
NK033(gi)003:991: dri med bdud rtsi 'byung ba dang //
NK033(gi)003:992: dgra bgegs srog rtsa gcod pa dang //
NK033(gi)003:993: dug lnga rtsad nas gcod pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)003:994: srog can rgyu dang srog med rgyu //
NK033(gi)003:995: 'di ni srog med rgyu yin te //
NK033(gi)003:996: snying rje med pas bsgral bar bya //
NK033(gi)003:998: tshogs phud tsho gsum du bcad de /
NK033(gi)003:999: dang po g.yas zhal dkar ba la dmigs la zhi ba'i lha tshogs la mchod /
NK033(gi)003:1000: gnyis pa g.yon dmar ba la dmigs la thugs rje gshe ba'i lha la bshags /
NK033(gi)003:1001: gsum pa dbus mthing ba la dmigs la khro bo
NK033(gi)003:1002: rngams pa'i lha tshogs la stob par bya ba'i dang
NK033(gi)003:1005: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa sbyar ba 'di //
NK033(gi)003:1006: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK033(gi)003:1007: dbang po lnga yi longs spyod mkho dgur ldan //
NK033(gi)003:1008: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK033(gi)003:1009: thugs dam bzhin du ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK033(gi)003:1011: gnyis pa thugs rje la dmigs nas bshags pa byas nas dbul ba ni /
NK033(gi)003:1013: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK033(gi)003:1014: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK033(gi)003:1015: lus kyis srog bcad sdig pa dngos su bgyis //
NK033(gi)003:1016: ngag gis rdzun smras gzhan la ngan du brjod //
NK033(gi)003:1017: sems kyis blo nor log par bsam la sogs //
NK033(gi)003:1018: 'dod khro gti mug dbang gis sdig pa ci bgyis pa //
NK033(gi)003:1019: bkram pa'i lha tshogs rnams la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)003:1020: ye shes lha la rtog pa mi mnga' yang //
NK033(gi)003:1021: de yi bka' 'khor gnas pa'i lha srin rnams //
NK033(gi)003:1022: 'di 'dra dmyal sogs shin tu mi bzod pas //
NK033(gi)003:1023: gnong zhing 'gal 'khrul mchis pa bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)003:1025: gsum pa zhal dbus mthing ba la dmigs te khro
NK033(gi)003:1026: bo khrag 'thung gi tshogs la stob pa bya ba
NK033(gi)003:1028: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
NK033(gi)003:1029: khams gsum ma lus za ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)003:1030: sha rus la sogs bza' bar bya //
NK033(gi)003:1032: nga ni khrag 'thung chen po ste //
NK033(gi)003:1033: 'khor ba'i d+r+wa bar chags pa dang //
NK033(gi)003:1034: dmar chen po la rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK033(gi)003:1035: 'khor gyi ma tshogs rnams dang rol //
NK033(gi)003:1036: dpal chen khrag 'thung he ru ka /
NK033(gi)003:1037: khro rgyal khrag 'thung rngams pa'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)003:1038: g.yo 'gul thams cad bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)003:1039: gzugs rnams thams cad he ru ka /
NK033(gi)003:1040: koo r+ai la sogs za byed rnams //
NK033(gi)003:1041: sed+ha la sogs gsod byed tshogs //
NK033(gi)003:1042: rta gdong la sogs 'ching sdom tshogs //
NK033(gi)003:1043: dbang phyug la sogs bka' nyan tshogs //
NK033(gi)003:1044: pho nya la sogs 'joms byed tshogs //
NK033(gi)003:1045: choms shig 'khor ba rtsad nas chom //
NK033(gi)003:1046: ha ha ru lu mchod pa bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1047: zhes zhal du bstab par bya'o //
NK033(gi)003:1048: de nas tshogs zan tha ma des dgra bgegs kyi ling+ga byas la bsgral ba ni /
NK033(gi)003:1049: sdang dgra gdon bgegs su dmigs te /
NK033(gi)003:1050: gnod byed kyi dug zhi bar byed pa'am /
NK033(gi)003:1051: nyon mongs pa dug lnga ru dmigs la /
NK033(gi)003:1053: 'khor ba rtsad nas gcod par bsam la bsgral te /
NK033(gi)003:1055: 'khor gyi dmag tshogs dam tshig can //
NK033(gi)003:1056: dam tshig tshul bzhin gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)003:1057: slob dpon la ni brnyas byed cing //
NK033(gi)003:1058: rdo rje spun la 'khu byed dang //
NK033(gi)003:1059: snying nas slob dpon smod byed rnams //
NK033(gi)003:1060: ma thogs myur du drag tu khug /
NK033(gi)003:1062: khro chung zhal gsum phyag drug pa //
NK033(gi)003:1063: mtshon cha'i rgyal po lcags kyu yis //
NK033(gi)003:1064: 'og min dga' ldan lha yul nas //
NK033(gi)003:1065: ngo mthon stobs kyis bsgral bar bya //
NK033(gi)003:1066: zhes brjod pas khro chung mang po 'phros nas dgra
NK033(gi)003:1067: bgegs gang na yod pa de lcags kyus bzung nas
NK033(gi)003:1068: gzugs de la thim par bsam mo //
NK033(gi)003:1069: de nas rang nyid lha'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas
NK033(gi)003:1070: bar chad bsal ba'i phyir mtshon cha sna tshogs kyis
NK033(gi)003:1072: khro bo'i lha tshogs la bstab par bya ste /
NK033(gi)003:1075: 'jigs byed chen po'i tshul ston pa //
NK033(gi)003:1076: dpal chen dgu dang yum chen dgu //
NK033(gi)003:1077: gnyis med sbyor ba'i byin rlabs las //
NK033(gi)003:1078: koo r+ai'i tshogs dang seng+ha'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)003:1079: sgo ma'i tshogs dang spor ma'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)003:1080: mkha' 'gro dbang phyug chen mo'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)003:1081: phung po dpal gyi zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)003:1082: 'byung ba yum gyi zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)003:1083: rnam shes koo r+ai'i zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)003:1084: yul ni phra men zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)003:1085: yan lag sgo ma'i zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)003:1086: rus pa mkha' 'gro'i zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)003:1087: khrag ni ma mo'i zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)003:1088: sha ni pho nya'i zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)003:1089: srog ni ging chen zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)003:1090: lhag ma 'khor gyi zhal du bstabs //
NK033(gi)003:1091: yas kyi bdud g.yos mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1092: mas kyi sri lang mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1093: pha khu'i rgan sri mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1094: ma bu'i byur 'dre mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1095: bu tsha'i phung sri mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1096: rnal 'byor dam sri mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1097: sdang ba'i dgra rnams mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1098: gnod pa'i bgegs rnams mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1099: sngags kyi sngags zor mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1100: chos kyi chos zor mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1101: bon gyi bon zor mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1102: rgya 'dre stong mtshams mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1103: rmi lam ngan pa mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1104: mtshan ma ngan pa mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1105: sbyor ba rtsub pa mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1106: lo skag zla zur mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1107: za skag bdun zhag mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1108: mi mthun phyogs rnams mchod par bzhes //
NK033(gi)003:1109: mchod bzhes dam skongs mthu rtsal dngos grub stsol //
NK033(gi)003:1110: zhes ling+ga gtub pa de gtor mar dbul lo //
NK033(gi)003:1111: bdun pa lhag ma mjug sdud kyi lung du lhag ma sdud cing gtor ma'i mjug bskyang ba'o //
NK033(gi)003:1112: de la phud dang lhag ma'i mtshams sbyor ba ni /
NK033(gi)003:1114: bcom ldan dpal chen 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK033(gi)003:1115: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i sku mnga' ba //
NK033(gi)003:1116: mi shigs sku yi dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)003:1117: chags med pad+ma 'dra ba'i spyan mnga' ba //
NK033(gi)003:1118: ma chags gsung gi dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)003:1119: 'gro drug thugs rjes sgrol ba'i thugs mnga' ba //
NK033(gi)003:1120: skye med thugs kyi dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)003:1121: 'gro drug smin mdzad bde ba'i don grub pa //
NK033(gi)003:1122: phrin las rtsal gyi dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK033(gi)003:1123: zhes brjod la mig btsum nas /
NK033(gi)003:1124: dmod bor la gtor ma'i nang nas gcig tog gis
NK033(gi)003:1125: blangs la dngos grub blangs pas sha la babs na
NK033(gi)003:1130: de nas rigs dbye ba ni /
NK033(gi)003:1131: mar king dbang phyug pho nya /
NK033(gi)003:1137: gnas ma dag gi shod du'o //
NK033(gi)003:1138: mgron dma' ba mar gyi gnas bdun longs spyod dman pa lhag /
NK033(gi)003:1141: byan mo'i tshul du brten pa'o //
NK033(gi)003:1142: bran mo dang g.yog mo'i tshul du brten pa'o //
NK033(gi)003:1143: de nas rang yi dam du bsgom /
NK033(gi)003:1144: ya rkan ma rkan gnyis rta mgrin yab yum gnyis su bsgom /
NK033(gi)003:1145: sbyor mtshams nas byang sems dkar dmar bdud rtsir phab ste gtor ma bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs /
NK033(gi)003:1148: nam mkha' stong la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK033(gi)003:1149: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis kyang //
NK033(gi)003:1151: rnam lnga'i longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK033(gi)003:1152: 'jig rten las kun khyod la bcol //
NK033(gi)003:1153: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK033(gi)003:1155: 'jig rten bya ba las grub pa'i //

NK033(gi)003:1540: bde chen gyi ngang la spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)003:1542: bcu gsum pa tshul shing gtad pa ni /
NK033(gi)003:1544: sangs rgyas rnams kyis chos bstan pa //
NK033(gi)003:1545: bden pa gnyis la yang dag bsten //
NK033(gi)003:1546: de bzhin kun rdzob bden pa dang //
NK033(gi)003:1547: dam pa'i don gyi bden pa'o //
NK033(gi)003:1548: sgra dang tshig kun rdzob yin /
NK033(gi)003:1550: don dam blo yi spyod yul min //
NK033(gi)003:1551: tshul chen 'di la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)003:1553: de nas tshig dbang byang sgor gur gum gyi chus
NK033(gi)003:1554: rdo rje rgya gram bris pa'i steng du slob ma
NK033(gi)003:1555: bzhag la tshig dbang rin po che 'di brjod par
NK033(gi)003:1558: e ma skye ba med pa /
NK033(gi)003:1561: rdzogs pa'i gnyis su med pa /
NK033(gi)003:1563: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK033(gi)003:1564: skyes tsam nyid nas skye ba med //
NK033(gi)003:1565: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK033(gi)003:1566: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK033(gi)003:1568: skye 'gags med pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK033(gi)003:1569: skye med kyi ngang du spyod pa'o //
NK033(gi)003:1570: tshul chen 'di la gnas par gyis //
NK033(gi)003:1575: bcu bzhi pa sgom thag gtad pa ni /
NK033(gi)003:1577: byams dang snying rje'i thugs mnga' zhing //
NK033(gi)003:1578: sangs rgyas phrin las bsgrub bya'i phyir //
NK033(gi)003:1579: bde ba'i bka' nan bde bcings nas //
NK033(gi)003:1580: chos dang chos nyid bsgom par gyis //
NK033(gi)003:1581: bu yi blo gros 'di gyis shig /
NK033(gi)003:1583: bco lnga pa sgom rten gtad pa ni /
NK033(gi)003:1585: rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob rig 'dzin chos sku'i gdung //
NK033(gi)003:1586: chos rje 'od dpag med pa bsgrub bya'i phyir //
NK033(gi)003:1587: bde ba'i lus la rab brten nas //
NK033(gi)003:1588: chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos phyir //
NK033(gi)003:1589: bu yi blo gros 'di gyis shig /
NK033(gi)003:1591: skabs 'dir byin gyis bla ma'i zhal shes /
NK033(gi)003:1594: de nas a ha ho'i bzhengs phyag spyi bor bzhag /
NK033(gi)003:1595: slob dpon gyi thugs ka nas 'od kyi gong bu gcig thon /
NK033(gi)003:1596: slob ma'i snying khar thim par bsam /
NK033(gi)003:1599: bcu drug pa mkha' 'gro ma la las gnyer gtad pa ni /
NK033(gi)003:1602: zhing las skyes kyi mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)003:1603: ming po rdo rje mched lcam la //
NK033(gi)003:1604: 'grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK033(gi)003:1605: byin rlabs chu bo'i rgyun ma bcad //
NK033(gi)003:1606: sgrub la bar du gcod pa'i bdud dgra rnams //
NK033(gi)003:1607: pha rol 'jigs pa'i stobs kyis med par mdzod //

NK033(gi)003:1609: mkha' 'gro ma yis bka' chad dbab par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)003:1610: mkha' la gshegs ma mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)003:1612: las las skyes kyi mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)003:1613: ming po rdo rje mched lcam la //

NK033(gi)003:1629: mkha' 'gro ma yis bka' chad dbab par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)003:1631: de nas rjes kyi cho ga la /
NK033(gi)003:1636: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje la //
NK033(gi)003:1637: ye shes lha yi dbang babs pas //
NK033(gi)003:1638: bka' brgyud ma chad pa yi babs //
NK033(gi)003:1640: bla ma lha la bzod par gsol //
NK033(gi)003:1641: byin gyi rlabs kyi chog khrigs 'di //
NK033(gi)003:1642: gang gis bskul nas su yis bkod //
NK033(gi)003:1643: sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs /
NK033(gi)003:1644: 'dzing rdo rje pra b+has tshigs bcad du sdebs pa rdzogs so ////
NK033(gi)003:1645: de nas gtor ma tsho gsum du bgos te /
NK033(gi)003:1646: chos dbyings kyi gtor ma gter du sbed pa ni /
NK033(gi)003:1648: thugs rje rang byung ye shes dkyil 'khor du //
NK033(gi)003:1649: snang srid mtshan ma'i bye brag kun //
NK033(gi)003:1650: snod kyi 'jig rten dbyings su sba //
NK033(gi)003:1651: snod kyang bcud kyi dbyings su sba //
NK033(gi)003:1652: snod bcud skye ba med par sba //
NK033(gi)003:1653: srid pa za byed gzhal yas khang //
NK033(gi)003:1654: rtsi shing bdud rtsi rang byung ste //
NK033(gi)003:1655: 'byung ba lnga dang rigs lnga yang //
NK033(gi)003:1656: chos nyid stong pa'i dbyings su sba //
NK033(gi)003:1657: nyon mongs dug lnga'i ngo bo yang //
NK033(gi)003:1658: ye shes lnga yi dbyings su sba //
NK033(gi)003:1659: ma rig 'khrul pa'i log rtog kyang //
NK033(gi)003:1660: mnyam snang chen po'i dbyings su sba //
NK033(gi)003:1661: rdzas rnams byang chub sems su bsgom //
NK033(gi)003:1662: sngags mkhan theg mchog rgyal por bsgom //
NK033(gi)003:1663: gnyis med gter du sba bar bya //
NK033(gi)003:1664: phyag rgya lnga yi rgya yis gdab //
NK033(gi)003:1665: de ltar sbas pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK033(gi)003:1666: yab yum lnga yi phyag sbrel la //
NK033(gi)003:1667: lu gu rgyud kyi bro brdung ngo //
NK033(gi)003:1668: gtor ma cha gcig po de dkyil 'khor gyi 'og tu gter du sba'o //
NK033(gi)003:1671: dngos grub 'byung ba'i dgos pa rnams yod pa yin no //
NK033(gi)003:1672: dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i mi zad pa'i gter du sba'o //
NK033(gi)003:1673: de nas ye shes rol pa'i gtor ma sbyin sreg tu 'bul ba ni /
NK033(gi)003:1674: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro rnams me thab kyi
NK033(gi)003:1675: gzhal yas khang du bskyed la me mchod dam sbyin
NK033(gi)003:1677: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i zhal du tshogs dang mchod pa 'bul lo //
NK033(gi)003:1678: thugs rje sprul pa'i gtor mas phyogs legs par dri
NK033(gi)003:1679: spos dang dri mchog bzang po ru man+dala legs pa
NK033(gi)003:1680: gcig byas la / de'i steng du gtor ma bzhag la /
NK033(gi)003:1681: 'gro ba rnams kyi don du bdag gis phan thogs
NK033(gi)003:1682: par bya ba'i phyir ram phrin las rnam bzhi'i don
NK033(gi)003:1683: grub par bya ba'i phyir gtor ma bskyang ba ni
NK033(gi)003:1685: shar nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun //
NK033(gi)003:1686: shar phyogs rdo rje rigs kyi bka' nyan tshogs //
NK033(gi)003:1687: drug ni rnal 'byor gral na bzhugs //
NK033(gi)003:1688: gcig ni thabs kyi sgo ma mdzad //
NK033(gi)003:1689: dkar mo dung gi mche ba can //
NK033(gi)003:1690: phyag na dung gi gzhong pa bsnams //
NK033(gi)003:1691: rgyan gyi gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK033(gi)003:1692: khyod kyis zhi ba'i las mdzod cig /
NK033(gi)003:1694: rgyu sbyor yon bdag pho mo yi //

NK033(gi)003:1734: gtor snod de rnams cha gsum du phye la /
NK033(gi)003:1735: cha gcig ma bshal bar kha yar bstan la bzhag /
NK033(gi)003:1736: nang du nas sam me tog gis bkang la /
NK033(gi)003:1738: des bkra shis pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK033(gi)003:1739: cha gcig bshal chu phyir dor /
NK033(gi)003:1740: bshal chu la re ba'i yi dwags tshim zhing kho thag chod pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK033(gi)003:1741: cha gcig mi bshal ba kha sbubs la /
NK033(gi)003:1742: dgra bgegs ting nge 'dzin gyi bkug la 'og tu bcug ste /
NK033(gi)003:1743: bro brdungs la mnan pa bya'o //
NK033(gi)003:1744: bar chad zhi nas dgra bgegs mi ldang ba'i dgos pa yod /
NK033(gi)003:1745: las kyi mjug bsdu bro brdung /
NK033(gi)003:1746: mnan pa byed pa'i dus su byin dbab cing /
NK033(gi)003:1748: dang po byin dbab pa ni /
NK033(gi)003:1749: a la la hoh b+ha ga w+aan /
NK033(gi)003:1750: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)003:1752: 'phags mchog thugs rje can gyi dus la bab //
NK033(gi)003:1753: khyad par bstan pa'i dus las bab //
NK033(gi)003:1754: dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i dus la bab //
NK033(gi)003:1755: byin chen dbab pa'i dus la bab //
NK033(gi)003:1756: mthu chen mthu rtsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK033(gi)003:1757: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK033(gi)003:1758: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK033(gi)003:1759: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK033(gi)003:1760: bdag cag las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK033(gi)003:1762: de nas bro brdung ba ni /
NK033(gi)003:1763: gtor gzhong kha sbubs pa'i 'og tu dgra bgegs bkug la /
NK033(gi)003:1765: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK033(gi)003:1766: kun kyang bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK033(gi)003:1767: bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam //
NK033(gi)003:1768: khro bo'i sprul pas nam mkha' gang //
NK033(gi)003:1769: khro mo'i sprul pas sa gzhi gang //
NK033(gi)003:1770: khro chung sprul pas bar snang gang //
NK033(gi)003:1771: ma mo mkha' 'gro dbyings na rol //
NK033(gi)003:1772: lta ba'i ngang la gnas pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)003:1773: bro ni bar chad med pa'i bro //
NK033(gi)003:1774: tshangs pa'i dbyangs su 'dren pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)003:1775: glu ni bar chad med par blangs //
NK033(gi)003:1776: dkyil 'khor rang la gnas pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)003:1777: tshig ni snying po 'dzab tu bgrang //
NK033(gi)003:1778: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:1779: nyon mongs lnga la bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)003:1780: dug lnga'i steng du sman lnga shar //
NK033(gi)003:1781: nga rgyal sa la bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)003:1782: nga rgyal spangs nas mnyam nyid shar //
NK033(gi)003:1783: 'dod chags chu la bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)003:1784: 'dod chags spangs nas bde chen shar //
NK033(gi)003:1785: zhe sdang me la bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)003:1786: zhe sdang spangs nas stong nyid shar //
NK033(gi)003:1787: phrag dog rlung la bro brdungs pa //
NK033(gi)003:1788: phrag dog spangs nas mnyam nyid shar //
NK033(gi)003:1789: gti mug nam mkhar bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)003:1790: gti mug spangs nas ye shes shar //
NK033(gi)003:1791: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)003:1792: khri gdugs brgya shar stong shar bas //
NK033(gi)003:1793: ye shes nyi ma gcig shar dro //
NK033(gi)003:1794: shar tsam nyid nas nub pa med //
NK033(gi)003:1795: nga ni dpal chen he ru ka /
NK033(gi)003:1796: rkang pa g.yas pas bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)003:1797: rnal 'byor pho sri mnan pa'i bro //
NK033(gi)003:1798: rkang pa g.yon pas bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)003:1799: rnal 'byor mo sri mnan pa'i bro //
NK033(gi)003:1800: rkang pa gnyis kas bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)003:1801: rgyab nyan rkun bu mnan pa'i bro //
NK033(gi)003:1802: rmig pa lcags kyis bro brdungs pas //
NK033(gi)003:1803: sa bdag sa srin mnan pa'i bro //
NK033(gi)003:1804: sba' ma de ni mi sba ru //
NK033(gi)003:1805: rgya mtsho chen po'i gting du sba //
NK033(gi)003:1806: mnan nam de ni mi mnan na //
NK033(gi)003:1807: ri rab chen po'i rmangs su mnan //
NK033(gi)003:1808: bskal pa brgyar yang ma ldang zhig /
NK033(gi)003:1810: rgya la 'da' na rdul du rlog /
NK033(gi)003:1812: s+t+wam b+ha rak+sha m+aa ra ya nan /
NK033(gi)003:1815: glu gar bro la sogs pas bkra shis pa'i rom mo bya'o //
NK033(gi)003:1816: rang don la ye shes pa mi gshegs //
NK033(gi)003:1817: gzhan don la ye shes pa gshegs so //
NK033(gi)003:1818: dam tshig gi lha gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa thugs kar bsdu /
NK033(gi)003:1825: de nas rdzogs rim brda bzhi la gsal gdab /
NK033(gi)003:1829: mngon rdzogs rgyal po yang dag gi gzhung gi phrin las rdzogs so ////
NK033(gi)003:1830: de ltar na zam pa'i byin rlabs bya tshul rang
NK033(gi)003:1831: 'dra'i blo dman rnams kyis go dka' bar mthong nas
NK033(gi)003:1832: khrigs chags su byas pa zhig byung na snyam pa
NK033(gi)003:1833: dang / nye char sprul pa'i sku mchog gnyis nas
NK033(gi)003:1834: kyang don gnyer chen pos bskul ma gnang don ltar
NK033(gi)003:1835: dang / / gzhung gi dgongs pa bzhin mngon rtogs
NK033(gi)003:1836: sgrub thabs ltar sbyar zhing cung zad gsal por btab
NK033(gi)003:1838: snyoms las pa 'gyur med tshe dbang mchog grub kyis
NK033(gi)003:1839: bris pa nyes 'gal mchis na chos bdag mkha' 'gro'i
NK033(gi)003:1840: tshogs kyis bzod par mdzad du gsol /
NK033(gi)003:1841: dge bas lam mchog 'di nyid mi nub par dar
NK033(gi)003:1842: zhing rgyas nas 'gro ba mtha' dag kun tu bzang
